    <div class="vessel-card-row"><span class="vessel-card-row-label">Infrastructure exists?</span><span class="vessel-card-row-val red">No</span></div>
    <div class="vessel-card-row"><span class="vessel-card-row-label">Draft at Kra terminals</span><span class="vessel-card-row-val red">Insufficient for VLCC</span></div>
